<template id="async">
    <button class="qure__faucet-button collapsed d-lg-none" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
        data-bs-target="#creative__direction" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="creative__direction">
        Post-Treatment Care & Tips
    </button>
    <div id="creative__direction" class="accordion-collapse collapse d-lg-block" aria-labelledby="creative__direction"
        data-bs-parent="#myTabContent">
        <div class="qure__faucet-body px-6 pb-30 pb-lg-0">
            <h2 class="d-md-block d-none qure__section-heading">Post-Treatment Care & Tips</h2>
            <p>After your Micro-Infusion treatment, your skin is more absorbent and sensitive.
                Following the right aftercare helps maximize results and minimize irritation.
            </p>
            <p class="fw-600">For the first 24 hours:</p>
            <ul class="list-dots ml-10 d-flex flex-column gap-1">
                <li>Stick to gentle skincare products only, such as hydrating cleansers and
                    simple moisturizers.</li>
                <li>Avoid makeup, sun exposure, heat (like saunas or workouts), and swimming.
                </li>
                <li>Skip active ingredients like retinol, acids, or vitamin C.</li>
                <li>Minimize touching your face – especially with unclean hands.</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="info_block fs-16 bg-primary-subtle p-15 rounded-10 d-flex mt-25 mw"
                style="--bs-primary-bg-subtle: #F4F8FD; --mw: 500px;">
                <div class="pr-10 mt-2">
                    <img src="https://qureskincaredns-main.com/assets/images/info_icon_blue.svg" alt="info icon blue">
                </div>
                <p>You may experience slight redness and irritation after the treatment. <span class="fw-600">This is
                        normal</span> and should subside within a few
                    hours!</p>
            </div>
            <div class="border-bottom my-30"></div>
            <p class="fw-600">The morning after:</p>
            <ul class="list-dots ml-10 d-flex flex-column gap-1">
                <li>Always apply SPF 50+ to protect your skin.</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="border-bottom my-30"></div>
            <p class="fw-600">For the next 2-3 days:</p>
            <ul class="list-dots ml-10 d-flex flex-column gap-1">
                <li>Gradually reintroduce your usual skincare.</li>
                <li>If you use exfoliants or actives (like retinol), wait 48–72 hours before
                    applying them again.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="https://qureskincaredns-main.com/assets/js/main-slider.js" defer></script>
    <script src="https://fast.wistia.com/assets/external/E-v1.js" defer></script>
</template>